### Create a new Fiat currency
POST http://localhost:3000/api/currency
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "symbol": "USD",
  "name": "US Dollar",
  "type": "Fiat",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Create a new Crypto currency
POST http://localhost:3000/api/currency
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "symbol": "ETH",
  "name": "Ethereum",
  "type": "Crypto",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Get all currencies (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currency

###

### Get all currencies with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currency?type=Fiat&isActive=true&page=1&perPage=10

###

### Get specific currency by symbol
GET http://localhost:3000/api/currency/USD

###

### Update a currency
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/currency
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "symbol": "USD",
  "name": "United States Dollar",
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Soft delete a currency
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/currency/USD
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Hard delete a currency (permanent)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/currency/USD?force=true
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
